des:
Voxprotocol.com presents, snackable sized 2 to 4-minute space-related audio missions that are created exclusively for Alexa device delivery with the hope of representing space history past to present to all generations of Travelers.

Our patent-pending audio software and ai music algorithms take all of the different audio files and types, stitches them together while rendering perfectly leveled voicefirst ready remastered audio output. This is how we deliver our listeners Voxprotocol's unrivaled sonic quality and create an incredible sense of presence as we situate them within these incredible environments.
